{"tid":1551096,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【威尼斯影展閉幕】香港導演楊凡贏最佳劇本 嘆港人失上街自由","createTime":"2019-09-07T23:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:43:57.000Z","uid":68738,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f955e1e63d15c157d5afa532ac081bbfa4f22bbb","tid":1551096,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190908/large/1567882785_1bc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190908%2Flarge%2F1567882785_1bc3.jpg&h=debc38d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊凡就以執導動畫《繼園臺七號》贏得最佳劇本，他上台領獎時表現興奮，並笑言：「我過去拍了14部作品，大家也在彈我的劇本無聊，但你們看！我現在拿了最佳劇本獎，我真的非常開心。」《繼園臺七號》故事發生在正值動盪的香港1967，楊凡之後嚴肅地稱在1964年從台灣來到香港，經歷了兩次轉變：「我也想感謝香港，給我所有自由讓我創作。我因為戒嚴從台灣來到香港，我在海邊就聞到自由，在街道就聞到自由。52年後，有股奇怪的力量影響了人權，讓人們甚至失去上街的自由、無法自由搭乘大眾交通工具。現時正如打開了潘朵拉盒子，但潘朵拉盒子中總會有希望，我希望香港可以回復正常，令我們可以再次感受自由。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190908/60021790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F60021790&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprnf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=b035e854\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F60021790&h=d1b93bd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190908/60021790</a>"},{"pid":"416a5c3b2eb70949dabfcc97221dc77b58e41db0","tid":1551096,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350f6678032eb097ab99489fc2dd8d